{"tid":500782,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"直播玩Air Tycoon Online 2番外篇5 - 講就易嘅Flight Sim","createTime":"2017-12-16T06:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T11:07:40.000Z","uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"18949c6944658c9a75ca4c610ae87c1afc5693bf","tid":500782,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:41:20.000Z","msg":"直播貼: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/426244/page/13\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/426244/page/13</a><br />\n番外篇1: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/486204/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/486204/page/1</a><br />\n番外篇2: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/491966/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/491966/page/1</a><br />\n番外篇3: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/494689/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/494689/page/1</a><br />\n番外篇4: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/495389/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/495389/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nATO2最為飛機迷津津樂道嘅賣點之一可能就Flight Sim, 每次成功降落加$1000, 失敗扣$100。降落者, 好Easy啦是咪? 你以為啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想要成功降落, 著地時需要達到幾項條件: 向前速要係140-160 kts之間, 垂直速度要係0至-1之間, 最後當然要成功係跑道尾前收停。<br />\n<br />\n講就真係好容易, 事實係我玩左十幾廿次都crash!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔知跌撚左幾多次$100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 亦令我好耐一段時間唔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過近排又有番鋪癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 哈哈, 反覆聽過唔同意見同睇完教學影片之後, 媽, 今次我終於得左啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U_lDau9onEg&amp;list=PLri_QYo_HVxjIs3JBtji9Hd0J1gXUWZBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwa